text: Did you remember we did the aero-modelling workshop in the first year together? That just seems yesterday. Thank you for helping me many times bro! Hope you achieve all the things you wish for! Cheers to lots of fun memories and a lifetime of friendship
author: Rudraraju Sai Vishnu Varma

text: Bhai Geetam kya maze kiye the yaar wo chahe tere room pe bulla kaatna ho, ya COD khelna ho, saath mei canteen jaana ho, har wednesday pizza khana ho, ya movie dekhna ho (Yaadh h "us" movie jisko tune tatti bola hðŸ˜‚) Mei apne room se zyada tere room pe rahtha tha! Socha nahi ki bina mile hi college khatam hojayega! All the best bro aage ke liye! Miltein rahenge

text:
Aur Bhai Khemraj kya bole yaar tumhare baare mei. Kitne memories h yaar jo kabhi bhool hi nahi paunga! Saath mei courses karna (yaadh h MOS exam ke pehle din poora raat tumhara kamare mei hi pade the ðŸ˜‚, aur robotics ka midsem ke din subah tumhara reaction tho epic tha ðŸ˜œ), roz raat ke ek baje canteen jaana, Pizza khana, Ya wing mei bulla kaatna, yaadh h diwali ke time mei horror series dekh raha tha aur power chala gaya tho mei darr ke maare tere kamre mei bhaag ke aaya ðŸ¤£, Intern ke tests ke liye bhi saath mei jaate the NCL aur kharab karne ke baadh saath mei rote the 

Bas ek cheez bolunga ek dho baar chillaya karo agar kamre saanp ya kuch aagaya tho kisi ko pata bhi nahi chalega! Aur all the best bhai aage ke liye waise tujhe zaroorat nahi tu anyway chaap dega! Apps banate raho aur bhejthe raho testing ke liye ðŸ˜…! Aur jab bhi kuch zaroorat tha tune hamesha madad kiya uske liye thanks (Wo hospital jaana yaadh h X-ray wala bandha Room number 40 bol raha tha ðŸ¤£). You are one of the most dependable person I ever met. Miltein rahenge bro
author: Rudraraju Sai Vishnu Varma

text:
Bhai KG first year mera room ke bagal mei tha lekin kabhi jyada baat hi nahi hui. Second year geetam ke room mei shuru hui thi bulla kaatna aur kitna memories bangaye yaar. Canteen ke liye saath mei jaana, Har wednesday pizza offer mei order karna, birthday parties ke liye liquid, CCD jaana.  Wo shailabh ko chappal utah ke bhagana aur laptop ko lekar ladai mei kabhi nahi bulunga ðŸ˜‚! Wo chahe party ho, bulla session ho, tere bina maza hi nahi aata tha
Kabhi socha hi nahi ki bina mile hi college khatam hojayega! Miltein rahne bro! All the best aage ke liye

text:
College sabse pehla jo dost bana tha wo tu tha bhai! Kitna masthi kiye the yaar! Aero-modelling workshop, Summer of Code, Aur wing mei bulla, birthday parties (jo tune mereko diya hi nahi kabhi ðŸ¤£ðŸ˜œ),  Tera wo Liquid wala incident mei kabhi nahi bhoolunga bhai! Saath mei milke prof ka bhi kaate the yaadh h ECO101 lene ke liye "Sir, I am interested in UPSC" bola aur tu bola finance wala shit. Codefundo mei jo bakwaas machaye the starting mei! Tumhari das hazar ki internship waali story tho epic tha bhai ðŸ¤£ðŸ¤£. Aur SOC mei apna idea ke liye kitna ladayi kiye the! Bhai tu bahut sahi bandha h yaar jo tujhe sahi lagtha h uske liye tu hamesha ladtha tha! Aur jab meri internship cancel hui thi bahut help kiye ho yaar wo sab kabhi bhool nahi paunga 
Bas ek cheez bolunga Photos mei jo colgate ki advertisement dete rahthe ho waise hi dete raho! Adobe mei jaake masthi karna! Kabhi aajao vizag, poora city ghumenge saath mei!
author: Rudraraju Sai Vishnu Varma

text: Assignment kiya kya? Wo topic pada h kya? Abhey yaar kitna tatti subject h bhai!! Isme pakka fail hone wala hoon!! aisa rote rote chaar saal kab khatam hua pata hi nahi chala! Pingala ka pre-registration se leke Exam ke baadh rone tak sab saath mei kiye the Bhai! Ye mechanical dept mei branch change karne ke baadh bas ek cheez accha hua wo ye h ki tere jaisa dost milgaya! Cheers Bro!
